description:
Former FDA Commissioner Dr. Scott Gottlieb peddles bullcrap to scare parents. Buck does an amazing analysis of Gottlieb's kid death counts for flu vs. covid. Joe suddenly says there's no federal solution to covid. Ron DeSantis effortlessly responds to the haters. C&B go to the phones, talk unreliable covid data, Antonio Brown with feisty and well-informed callers.
